name: formulas-split
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.4" %}

{% set build_number = 0 %}

package:
  name: formulas-split
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/vinci1it2000/formulas/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d3566c80f2df33cab532a6f97aa595b39da6faed543ccb508617316b8efb89c8

build:
  noarch: python
  number: {{ build_number }}

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6

test:
  commands:
    - echo "tests in subpackages"

outputs:
  - name: formulas
    build:
      noarch: python
      number: {{ build_number }}
      script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - numpy >=1.15
        - python >=3.6
        - python-dateutil
        - numpy-financial
        - regex
        - schedula >=1.2.18
    test:
      requires:
        - pip
      imports:
        - formulas
      commands:
        - pip check

  - name: formulas-excel
    build:
      noarch: python
      number: {{ build_number }}
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage('formulas', max_pin='x.x.x') }}
        - openpyxl
        - python >=3.6
    test:
      requires:
        - pip
      imports:
        - formulas.excel
      commands:
        - pip check

  - name: formulas-plot
    build:
      noarch: python
      number: {{ build_number }}
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage('formulas', max_pin='x.x.x') }}
        - docutils
        - flask
        - jinja2
        - pygments
        - python >=3.6
        - python-graphviz
    test:
      requires:
        - pip
      commands:
        - pip check

  - name: formulas-all
    build:
      noarch: python
      number: {{ build_number }}
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage('formulas-excel', max_pin='x.x.x') }}
        - {{ pin_subpackage('formulas-plot', max_pin='x.x.x') }}
        - python >=3.6
    test:
      source_files:
        - test
        - setup.cfg
      requires:
        - ddt
        - dill
        - nose >=1.0
        - pip
      commands:
        - pip check
        - rm test/test_readme.py test/test_setup.py  # [unix]
        - del test\test_readme.py test\test_setup.py  # [win]
        - nosetests

about:
  home: https://github.com/vinci1it2000/formulas
  license: EUPL-1.1
  license_family: OTHER
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Parse and compile Excel formulas and workbooks in python code.
  doc_url: https://formulas.readthedocs.io

extra:
  feedstock-name: formulas
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
